      "title": "Community Kitchen by Central Colombo launched",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The first community kitchen concept was launched today at the Samagipura housing scheme at Grandpass with a view to help provide a meal for the people with low income families. The concept was introduced by Colombo Mayoress Rosy Senanayake to prepare and share healthy, affordable meals among low-income city dwellers who have been severely affected by the crisis. Pix by Samantha Perera"
